# Stage 1: Tokenization

Lexical recognition and source locations only.

## Contract

- Input: source text and a merged directive registry
- Output: located tokens and lexical diagnostics
- Decides: token boundaries, source locations, delimiter context, directive tokens
- Must not decide: types, imports, constants, template semantics, numeric failure modes
- Invariant: tokenization never needs semantic facts

## Main paths

- `src/compiler_frontend/tokenizer/lexer.rs`
- `src/compiler_frontend/numeric_text/`

